		<description><![CDATA[A Look at the Profitability of Email List Building For Marketers When you type in to Google or Yahoo! the phrase: &#8220;the money is in the list&#8221; you&#8217;ll find over 2 billion results. So we can agree that it can be considered to be the reality. Nonetheless many internet marketers do miss plenty of email [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>A Look at the Profitability of Email List Building For Marketers</strong></p>
<p>When you type in to Google or Yahoo! the phrase: &#8220;the money is in the list&#8221; you&#8217;ll find over 2 billion results. So we can agree that it can be considered to be the reality. Nonetheless many internet marketers do miss plenty of email list building opportunities, however it could be easily done. If you would like to take your business to the next level you need to make certain you are grabbing every single opportunity to capture leads.</p>
<p>Get people hooked &#8211; A lot of online marketers swear to free give away squeeze pages when it comes to list building, nevertheless there are a few other points to consider, too. For instance you can arrange a web seminar about a burning problem your customers are facing and invite as many men and women as possible using social media and social bookmarking. By signing up to the free webinar your prospective customers will think they&#8217;re special to be included in the list of invited persons and will not for a moment think that you want their email address to market them. They&#8217;ll understand that you actually need to have their email address to send them a few reminders, but make sure you clearly state what else you are using their e-mail for.</p>
<p>Keep them engaged &#8211; They say that getting prospects is the simple part: handling all of them is much harder than that. Make sure you&#8217;re using the basic rule of e-mail marketing: 75% of content and 25% of marketing. When you get the balance right and don&#8217;t send out two-to-three marketing emails every day it is possible to keep your subscribers engaged. You can also make certain that you upload more free content on your web site that&#8217;s only offered for subscribers to make them really feel unique. You&#8217;ll be able to keep them motivated by creating &#8220;subscribers only&#8221; bonuses or offers.</p>
<p>Do not hand out leads &#8211; Make certain that when you are advertising an affiliate product you&#8217;re capturing leads before you would send them over to the affiliate site. Otherwise if they are not signing up you will never see them again, and you simply wasted your time.</p>
<p>Never abuse your list &#8211; After email list building, make sure you are not sending out unnecessary e-mails to your list. Just because an offer pays effectively it does not mean your mailing list is going to be interested. You also need to make certain you&#8217;re not promoting a good value product to giveaway seekers, however if a client has acquired a  product from you the next step is not a free gift but a  product upsell.</p>
